# Object Property: pbpko:RO_0002263 (acts upstream of)

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:RO_0002263 "c acts upstream of p if and only if c enables some f that is involved in p' and p' occurs chronologically before p, is not part of p, and affects the execution of p. c is a material entity and f, p, p' are processes.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label pbpko:RO_0002263 "acts upstream of")
SubObjectPropertyOf(pbpko:RO_0002263 pbpko:RO_0002264)

# Object Property: pbpko:RO_0002264 (acts upstream of or within)

