AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:PBPKO_00442 "A partition coefficient representing the ratio of compound concentration in milk to plasma.")
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:PBPKO_00442 "0000-0001-8345-1349")
