# Individual: pbpko:OBI_0002235 (pT1 (lung))

AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000115 pbpko:OBI_0002235 "A pathologic primary tumor stage for lung according to AJCC 7th edition indicating that the tumor is 3 cm or less in greatest dimension, surrounded by lung or visceral pleura without bronchoscopic evidence of invasion more proximal than the lobar bronchus (i.e., not in the main bronchus)."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(pbpko:IAO_0000117 pbpko:OBI_0002235 "Chris Stoeckert, Helena Ellis")
